#: ../../c-api/veryhigh.rst:42
msgid ""
"This is a simplified interface to :c:func:`PyRun_AnyFileExFlags` below, "
"leaving the *flags* argument set to ``NULL``."
msgstr ""
"Esta ĂŠ uma interface simplificada para :c:func:`PyRun_AnyFileExFlags` "
